This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning, specifically with word embeddings and bias mitigation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves probabilistic modeling, which suggests that it could also fit into cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with AI and bias, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves cybersecurity, which could place it in cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Finally, the paper involves probabilistic observations, which could place it in cs.CY (Computers and Society).
